      "date": "2013-05-03 12:38:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/cba593e2-b3e4-11e2-b8f6-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
